ing the finishing line at the Stade de France andBBC host Gabby Logan suggested he had made a 'selfish decision'by competing and putting the other athletes at risk.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabby Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"hugging\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow competitors\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"the finishing line\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'selfish decision'by\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the other athletes\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Johnson, meanwhile, said he was 'morally' unsure about Lyles' decision to embrace Bednarek, especially given the latter is due to run for the United States in the 4x100m relay on Friday.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 993, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso